Name: Blighted Fang
AttributesDescription: A calcified fang-shaped remnant of the Dark Tide creatures. Can be used to advance reward progress in Hunters' Rite.
BgDescription: A calcified fragment left behind by the Dark Tide creatures, shaped like a beast's fang. Though affected by Tidal Blight, it poses no threat and holds no practical purpose. To most, it's just another forsaken shard scattered across the Plateaus. But to Gladiators, Blighted Fangs carry meaning. Hunters who clash with the Dark Tide often claim these fangs from fallen Dark Tide creatures before they dissolve. Each fang is a blood-earned token of valor and a silent yet gleaming badge of honor.
